temp-watch (ver 1.2)
=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Various compatibility updates to mudge's old school temp-watch tool that
was released during his time with the (now) infamous L0pht Heavy Industries
(the original hacker-space.)  Forward-porting modifications for Linux 
applied by Derek Callaway <decal@ethernet.org> ...

Tested on: Ubuntu 14.04.3 LTS 
Linux ca2 3.13.0-49-generic SMP x86_64 GNU/Linux

Linux Compile: make linux

BSD Compile: make bsd

Clean: make clean
       (removes object files and core dumps, but leaves binary)

Clobber: make clobber
       (remove the same things as clean, and the binary as well)
